{
  "name": "newapi-bar",
  "displayName": "NewAPI Bar",
  "description": "New-API balance & usage in your status bar",
  "version": "0.0.1",
  "publisher": "local",
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.60.0"
  },
  "activationEvents": [
    "onStartupFinished"
  ],
  "main": "./extension.js",
  "contributes": {
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "newapiStatus.refresh",
        "title": "New API: Refresh Status"
      }
    ],
    "configuration": {
      "title": "New API Status",
      "properties": {
        "newapiStatus.baseUrl": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "New-API instance base URL"
        },
        "newapiStatus.token": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "System access token"
        },
        "newapiStatus.userId": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 0,
          "description": "User ID"
        },
        "newapiStatus.refreshInterval": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 60,
          "description": "Auto refresh interval (minutes)"
        },
        "newapiStatus.slides": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "default": [
            "$(credit-card) ${today} / ${balance}",
            "$(graph) ${percent} ${bar}",
            "$(history) ${total_requests} reqs  $(zap)${rpm}rpm"
          ],
          "markdownDescription": "状态栏轮播内容，每项依次显示。支持 VSCode 图标 `$(icon-name)` 和以下占位符：\n\n| 占位符 | 说明 |\n|---|---|\n| `${balance}` | 余额 如 $2.85 |\n| `${balance_tokens}` | 余额 tokens 数 |\n| `${today}` | 今日消耗 |\n| `${today_tokens}` | 今日消耗 tokens |\n| `${today_requests}` | 今日请求次数 |\n| `${monthly}` | 本月消耗 |\n| `${monthly_tokens}` | 本月消耗 tokens |\n| `${used}` | 累计消耗 |\n| `${total}` | 总额（余额+消耗）|\n| `${percent}` | 余额百分比 |\n| `${bar}` | 进度条 ████░░ |\n| `${total_requests}` | 累计请求次数 |\n| `${rpm}` | 每分钟请求数 |\n| `${tpm}` | 每分钟 tokens |\n| `${update_time}` | 上次更新时间 |"
        },
        "newapiStatus.slideInterval": {
          "type": "number",
          "default": 4,
          "description": "Seconds between carousel slides"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}